{
  "texts": [
    "We did not include some PROBAST signaling questions because they are not relevant to generative AI models.",
    "Details of modifications made to PROBAST are in Appendix Table S1 (online).",
    "We calculated the pooled accuracy of diagnosis brought by generative AI models and physicians based on the previously reported studies.",
    "The pooled diagnosis accuracies were compared between all AI models and overall physicians using the multivariable random-effect meta-regression model with adjustment for medical speciality, task of models, type of test dataset, level of bias, and publication status.",
    "In addition to the comparison of all AI models and overall physicians, we compared each AI model with overall physicians and each AI model with each physician experience level (expert or non-expert)."
  ]
}